automaticAccessEnabled() - Method in class com.ixortalk.udini.android.sdk.UdiniOptions
Whether or not the SDK should allow automatic access when the mobile device comes in range of an Udini device configured with an invoke-on-proximity setting.

When this is true it will allow users to unlock doors and trigger actions by coming in the vicinity of an Udini device, which is particularly convenient for lower-security and frequently accessed gateways.

Defaults to true.
